hment experiment: carbon cycling in high- and low-Si waters (2004) Science, 304, pp. 408-417; Mengesha, S., Dehairs, F., Fiala, M., Elskens, M., Goeyens, L., Seasonal variations of phytoplankton community structure and nitrogen uptake regime in the Indian sector of the Southern Ocean (1998) Polar Biol., 20, pp. 259-272; Semeneh, M., Dehairs, F., Elskens, M., Baumann, M.E.M., Kopczynska, E.F., Lancelot, C., Goeyens, L., Nitrogen uptake regime and phytoplankton community structure in the Atlantic and Indian sectors of the Southern Oceans (1998) J. Mar. Syst., 17, pp. 159-177; Sambrotto, R.N., Mace, B.J., Coupling of biological and physical regimes across the Antarctic polar front as reflected by nitrogen production and recycling (2000) Deep Sea Res. II, 47, pp. 3339-3367","Prakash, S.; Physical Research Laboratory, Navrangpura, Ahmedabad 380 009, India; email: satyap@incois.gov.in",,,,,,,,00113891,,CUSCA,,"English","Curr. Sci.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-78650027474
